<HEAD>La Toya Jackson Collpases From Jet Lag</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CARACAS, Venezuela (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   La Toya Jackson, big sister to
pop-singer Michael Jackson, collapsed from jet lag after her flight
here from Italy, it was reported Wednesday.
   Reporters and fans converged on a Caracas hotel where La Toya was
staying, hoping to get a glimpse of the woman who has stirred
interest with a series of nude photographs appearing in Playboy
magazine, according to daily El Diario.
   La Toya arrived Tuesday to appear on a TV variety show titled
``Only for Men.''
   La Toya collapsed following the 30-hour flight from Rome and
could not attend a Tuesday news conference, said manager Jack
Gordons.
