<HEAD>Borden Purchases Three Small Businesses</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Borden Inc., continuing an aggressive expansion
program, said Wednesday it had acquired three small food businesses
in other countries.
   The food, consumer and industrial products company said it had
purchased a small West German bakery, Gross; the United Maple
Products business of the Canadian company John Labatt Ltd.; and the
